@startuml
state WaitingForCard
state InvalidCard
state EnterPin
state IncorrectPin
state CorrectPin
state Options
state WithdrawMoney
state CheckInfo
state Transfer
state SecurityHold
state CancelOperation

[*]WaitingForCard --> EnterPin: CardInserted
EnterPin --> CorrectPin: ValidPIN
EnterPin --> IncorrectPin: InvalidPIN
IncorrectPin --> IncorrectPin: TryAgain
IncorrectPin -- 3* IncorrectPin: SecurityHold
CorrectPin --> Options: ValidUser
Options --> WithdrawMoney: WithdrawSelected
Options --> CheckInfo: InfoSelected
Options --> Transfer: TransferSelected
CancelOperation --> WaitingForCard: UserCancelled
@enduml
